how it all ended today.

18:19.832 --> 18:20.833
Neither did I.

18:22.668 --> 18:24.002
But I'm partly right, am I not?

18:25.337 --> 18:26.538
Partly.

18:27.773 --> 18:29.108
What happens?

18:30.809 --> 18:31.944
Nothing.

18:33.145 --> 18:34.947
It bothers me
that you know me so well.

18:35.013 --> 18:36.615
That you get me figured out.

18:37.549 --> 18:39.318
It makes me feel miserable.

18:40.752 --> 18:43.088
I think you do it all for you.

18:45.491 --> 18:49.128
But it is all right too.
It is valuable research.

18:49.194 --> 18:50.696
You didn't say that today.

18:50.762 --> 18:55.134
I was a bit upset.

18:55.701 --> 18:57.069
Upset?

18:58.837 --> 19:00.205
Like crazy?

19:01.874 --> 19:03.242
Yes, crazy about you.

19:05.244 --> 19:06.778
Come here and I'll show you.

19:07.613 --> 19:08.480
Where to?

19:09.148 --> 19:10.482
