19:13.785 --> 19:16.488
You wanted to have sex.

19:20.826 --> 19:22.161
Guess what I'm wearing.

19:27.232 --> 19:28.233
Shorts?

19:30.335 --> 19:31.336
And below?

19:32.671 --> 19:33.739
Nothing.

19:35.674 --> 19:37.209
You are a bad boy.

19:43.415 --> 19:44.816
Guess what I am doing.

19:47.019 --> 19:48.220
You're touching yourself.

19:53.458 --> 19:54.726
Are you in a hurry?

19:57.129 --> 20:01.733
You're arriving at the station.
I know you too. You see?

20:05.504 --> 20:06.738
Really?

20:09.141 --> 20:10.409
What am I thinking?

20:11.510 --> 20:13.045
You want me to eat your mouth.

20:16.148 --> 20:17.449
What are you doing?

20:18.383 --> 20:19.685
What do you want me to do?

20:20.886 --> 20:22.788
Put your hand under my shorts.

20:25.524 --> 20:27.192
Push hard.

20:28.126 --> 20:29.428
Is that okay?

20:30.529 --> 20:33.565
Yes. Now bite me.

20:35.801 --> 20:36.868
Where?

20:37.402 --> 20:38.503
My neck.

20:38.837 --> 20:40.339
Is this okay?

20:43.609 --> 20:44.910
Now the breasts.

20:46.612 --> 20:48.547
The nipples, right?

20:48.614 --> 20:49.615
Keep going down.

20:49.948 --> 20:53.418
I'll go down.
Is that okay?

20:55.287 --> 20:56.722
Get it in, Lucio.

20:59.725 --> 21:01.426
Fuck me!

21:04.263 --> 21:06.965
Do you like it this way?
Harder?

21:07.599 --> 21:08.900
Yes.

21:21.146 --> 21:22.114
Damn!

21:24.750 --> 21:25.784
What happened?

21:25.851 --> 21:27.953
I have to go.
The bell's ringing.

21:32.024 --> 21:33.925
Call me tomorrow, will you?

21:37.162 --> 21:38.196
Bye.

21:56.248 --> 21:58.717
Marisa told me
you went to see her.

21:59.051 --> 22:00.852
Yes, she is lovely.
She helped me a lot.

22:00.919 --> 22:01.987
About the trains?

22:03.555 --> 22:06.825
-Yes.
-Federico told me.

22:07.993 --> 22:09.161
Yes, about that.

22:09.227 --> 22:10.762
How much time do you have
to hand in a story?

22:11.129 --> 22:12.998
Do you have a deadline?

22:13.065 --> 22:15.033
Sometimes you do.
It depends.

22:15.100 --> 22:16.201
Some stories take longer
than others.

22:16.535 --> 22:18.937
Some stories must be
more difficult than others.

22:19.004 --> 22:21.106
And some reporters are
more dedicated than others.

22:21.473 --> 22:23.041
It depends on several things.

22:23.375 --> 22:26.311
-What is this story about?
-She's just said it.

22:27.079 --> 22:29.715
Something about trains.
What in particular?

22:30.082 --> 22:31.283
I'd rather not talk
much about it.

22:31.350 --> 22:33.518
Children hit by trains.

22:33.585 --> 22:37.122
-The boy is listening, dad!
-I'm sorry.

22:37.189 --> 22:39.825
It's not just that.
There is much more to it.

22:40.459 --> 22:41.893
What else?

22:42.527 --> 22:43.862
