But there is a lot more.

22:44.196 --> 22:45.997
If you don't know,
so far it's about...

22:46.064 --> 22:48.233
children hit by trains, honey.

22:49.167 --> 22:50.969
I'm done.
Can I go play?

22:51.036 --> 22:53.839
Have you had enough?

22:54.272 --> 22:56.141
Sure?
Okay, you can go.

22:59.711 --> 23:01.780
I've got you some candy.

23:06.651 --> 23:08.019
What are you upset about?

23:08.353 --> 23:10.889
Me?
About nothing.

23:11.423 --> 23:12.891
You seem to be upset
about something.

23:13.225 --> 23:15.060
Did I say something wrong?

23:15.127 --> 23:17.028
It is not what you say
but the tone you use.

23:17.095 --> 23:19.498
-What tone, honey?
-That damn tone of yours.

23:19.564 --> 23:21.199
Stop it, Verónica!

23:23.902 --> 23:26.238
Who is this, auntie?

23:27.773 --> 23:28.874
A friend of mine.

23:28.940 --> 23:31.109
Look, dad.
Is this from Rayo Vallecano?

23:31.176 --> 23:32.210
Let me see.

23:33.311 --> 23:35.914
Yes, exactly.
Rayo Vallecano.

23:36.314 --> 23:38.817
The Spanish team.
But look closer.

23:40.886 --> 23:42.788
His t-shirt reads
Rayito Vallecano.

23:46.057 --> 23:48.393
Can I see it?

23:48.994 --> 23:50.562
Rayito Vallecano...

23:53.632 --> 23:55.867
He used to play so well.

23:56.268 --> 23:59.171
Yes, he should've been
in the major leagues.

23:59.538 --> 24:01.440
We would all be rich now.

24:01.773 --> 24:03.341
Do you remember
that unforgettable match?

24:03.742 --> 24:05.944
-Do you remember it?
-Yes, I was there.

24:06.611 --> 24:08.447
He stopped the ball
in the middle of the field.

24:08.847 --> 24:12.083
He kicked it over the goal.
Too bad he's such a mess.

24:12.417 --> 24:13.652
We could be in Europe
enjoying the good stuff.

24:13.985 --> 24:16.121
Not this damn thing!
Where did you buy it?

24:17.055 --> 24:18.089
At the usual place.

24:18.156 --> 24:19.825
I told you
not to go there anymore.

24:23.562 --> 24:25.197
There you are.

24:25.530 --> 24:28.467
Here is some for you, girls.

24:28.533 --> 24:29.835
How long have you been clean?

24:30.202 --> 24:31.636
Seven months.

24:31.703 --> 24:33.271
It must be hard for you
to resist, right?

25:22.153 --> 25:23.655
What are you doing, punk?

25:23.722 --> 25:26.057
Shut up, idiot.
I'll beat you up.

25:26.958 --> 25:28.093
Damn you!

25:31.963 --> 25:32.898
What are you looking at?

25:33.632 --> 25:34.566
Go to hell!

25:38.103 --> 25:41.406
Yes, Nahuel.
I remember him very well.

25:41.740 --> 25:45.243
A good boy.
A bit rough for soccer.

25:45.610 --> 25:49.047
Good-hearted.
He must be in one of these.

25:51.683 --> 25:52.751
Do you know what happened
to him?

25:53.084 --> 25:55.620
I haven't seen him
for a long time.

25:55.954 --> 25:58.356
He stopped coming
about a year ago.

25:58.723 --> 26:00.258
What happened to him?

26:01.393 --> 26:04.296
He was hit by a train.
He died.

26:10.101 --> 26:12.470
Here he is.

26:14.539 --> 26:16.474
Why did the stop coming?

26:18.243 --> 26:19.377
He kicked
all the other players.

26:19.711 --> 26:21.413
He was sent to the bench
every time.

26:22.113 --> 26:26.084
His category was overcrowded.

26:26.418 --> 26:27.652
He rarely got to play.

26:27.986 --> 26:31.022
He used to live in a slum,
Los Piletones.

26:31.356 --> 26:33.525
I don't know.

26:33.858 --> 26:36.861
They fill out a form
when they start playing.

26:37.195 --> 26:39.831
But when they stop playing,
we tear it off.

26:40.932 --> 26:43.768
Could he have gone
to another club?

26:44.135 --> 26:46.905
Yes, there are many soccer
clubs in this area.

26:47.238 --> 26:52.310
Could be.
Was it an accident?

27:06.758 --> 27:09.361
Come here, Peque.

27:12.464 --> 27:13.732
Raise hell.

27:15.500 --> 27:17.002
With the new guy.

27:24.643 --> 27:26.077
Hey, you!

27:28.847 --> 27:30.682
Come on!
Keep playing, ladies.

27:43.928 --> 27:44.996
This is for you.
It's 5,000 pesos.

27:45.397 --> 27:46.564
Thanks a lot.

27:46.631 --> 27:47.966
You did your job well.
I said I'd help you out.

27:48.033 --> 27:49.234
I've got enough
to make a downpayment.

27:49.668 --> 27:51.870
Give some coke to the new boy.
It's on the house.

27:51.936 --> 27:54.806
-Thanks, Rivero.
-What is it, Peque?

27:54.873 --> 27:56.441
When is the next competition?

27:56.875 --> 27:59.310
-You ran out of money yet?
-That's my business.

27:59.644 --> 28:01.746
I don't set the dates
of the competitions.

28:02.947 --> 28:04.349
Don't worry.
It will be soon enough.

28:04.416 --> 28:05.817
Will it be
against Cholito again?

28:05.884 --> 28:08.887
No, he lost. He is out.
It's like a golden goal.

28:08.953 --> 28:10.689
If you lose, you are out.

28:10.755 --> 28:12.424
-I'm not gonna lose.
-Great.

28:12.791 --> 28:15.293
I want more money.
Last time you gave me peanuts.

28:15.360 --> 28:16.594
Come on!

28:16.661 --> 28:19.297
I saw many people there.
I want at least 2,000.

28:19.364 --> 28:20.532
Do you know how much that is?

28:20.865 --> 28:22.300
There is no competition then.

28:26.771 --> 28:28.940
I'll see what I can do.
Go practise now.

29:11.049 --> 29:13.051
-Catch her!
-No! Wait!

29:13.451 --> 29:16.855
-Give me your bag!
-No! Wait!

29:21.960 --> 29:23.728
Damn!

29:40.211 --> 29:43.414
You're so silly!
Don't forget about the tires.

29:43.815 --> 29:45.083
What tires?

29:45.984 --> 29:47.752
Are you kidding me?

29:48.186 --> 29:52.123
I walked by the shop yesterday
and they were lying there.

29:52.757 --> 29:56.528
If the guy buys another dog,
we will be doomed.

29:58.997 --> 30:00.698
I don't care.
I have another competition.

30:01.099 --> 30:02.467
-When?
-I don't know.

30:02.801 --> 30:04.369
But I'll have another one.
Because I won.

30:04.702 --> 30:07.372
And if I win this one,
I'll get 2,000.

30:08.940 --> 30:11.109
-Is it about soccer?
-It's about being brave.

30:11.176 --> 30:12.777
Stop it.
I can't tell you anything else.

30:13.211 --> 30:14.312
You compete against another boy?

30:14.646 --> 30:16.815
Of course.
Against Cholito.

30:17.148 --> 30:18.149
The guy you met at the club.

30:18.483 --> 30:20.852
He lost.

30:21.486 --> 30:23.221
So he can't compete anymore.

30:23.955 --> 30:24.889
He is out.

30:25.223 --> 30:26.691
Why don't you compete
against me?

30:26.758 --> 30:28.426
No matter who wins,
we'll split the money.

30:28.760 --> 30:30.695
-It is convenient, isn't it?
-Could be.

30:31.129 --> 30:32.630
Sure.

30:34.098 --> 30:36.634
Let me compete first
and then we'll see.

30:37.068 --> 30:38.536
Okay.

30:42.807 --> 30:44.209
Give me some.

30:46.945 --> 30:48.880
I'll come back quickly.
It is not far away.

30:48.947 --> 30:50.381
You're kidding me?
It's at the end of the world.

30:50.448 --> 30:53.785
Can I have your mobile number?
My phone was stolen.

30:53.852 --> 30:54.886
What happened?

30:54.953 --> 30:55.987
Nothing.
It is a long story.

30:56.054 --> 30:58.122
I'll send it to you
through Whatsapp.

30:59.624 --> 31:02.894
-Don't smoke in the car.
-I won't. Thanks.

31:04.429 --> 31:06.064
Stretch it a bit more.

31:06.497 --> 31:08.333
So there will be fewer wrinkles.

31:08.666 --> 31:11.536
That means less ironing. Did
you put a clothes' pin there?

31:11.603 --> 31:14.172
-Yes, I got it.
-And now this one.

31:15.106 --> 31:17.809
-Here?
-Yes, stretch it.

31:18.643 --> 31:20.712
-Perfect.
-Hello.

31:22.780 --> 31:24.782
-I've brought you this.
-Thanks, dad.

31:24.849 --> 31:26.150
-How are you?
-Fine.

31:26.885 --> 31:30.288
Can I have a word with your mom?

31:32.090 --> 31:33.291
What are you doing here?
What do you want?

31:34.492 --> 31:35.860
I am moving out.

31:37.128 --> 31:38.596
To an apartment near here.

31:39.097 --> 31:40.231
It is small.
A studio.

31:40.565 --> 31:44.435
I can put a partition
and a bed for Martina.

31:44.502 --> 31:47.038
Why are you doing this to me,
Rafael?

31:47.105 --> 31:50.742
I am not doing anything to you.
I only want to be with Martina.

31:50.808 --> 31:54.279
I want her to visit me.
I want her to have a room.

31:54.345 --> 31:55.947
I don't want to argue.

31:57.282 --> 31:59.417
I know you.
I know you'll insist.

32:00.618 --> 32:03.288
Fine, move
to your new apartment.

32:03.354 --> 32:05.356
Have a room for Martina.
Do what you want.

32:05.690 --> 32:08.927
But listen to me.
I'll be watching you.

32:09.260 --> 32:12.597
And if you screw up,
even once,

32:12.664 --> 32:15.300
I swear on my life
you won't see her again.

32:17.402 --> 32:20.004
-Thanks.
-Go to hell.

32:30.148 --> 32:31.549
Your father got you only one?

32:34.519 --> 32:36.688
How are you, Peque?

32:36.754 --> 32:38.356
What are you doing here?
Has Rivero sent you?

32:38.423 --> 32:40.191
-He is my father.
-I am Martina's father.

32:41.693 --> 32:43.127
Where did you two meet?

32:43.194 --> 32:45.897
Peque is one of the club's
best defenders.

32:45.964 --> 32:47.098
The club where I work.

32:47.665 --> 32:49.133
Yes, your father got me there.

32:49.200 --> 32:50.368
I saw him play in the park.

32:50.435 --> 32:51.769
I told him
he could take a test.

32:52.370 --> 32:53.438
I have to leave, honey.

32:54.105 --> 32:55.373
Go inside.
You mother is looking for you.

32:55.707 --> 32:57.608
-Will I see you again?
-Yes, you will.

32:59.277 --> 33:01.980
-Bye, dad. I love you.
-Me too.

33:02.680 --> 33:03.815
See you tomorrow.

33:07.185 --> 33:08.920
-Ask him.
-What?

33:08.987 --> 33:10.254
If I can compete against you.

33:10.621 --> 33:11.756
I don't know
if he knows about that.

33:12.757 --> 33:14.292
Of course he does.

33:48.126 --> 33:49.794
Are you Mr. Corso?

33:51.162 --> 33:52.764
Who wants to know?

33:54.165 --> 33:55.833
My name is Verónica Rosenthal.

33:55.900 --> 33:56.968
At the police station
they told me...

33:57.035 --> 33:58.269
I could find you here.

33:59.203 --> 34:00.605
A reporter.

34:01.272 --> 34:02.740
How could you tell?

34:05.043 --> 34:06.477
I work for "Nuestro Tiempo".

34:07.512 --> 34:09.580
-A newspaper?
-No, a magazine.

34:10.248 --> 34:11.516
I don't know it.

34:13.017 --> 34:16.921
My mother loved puzzles.
We made them together.

34:20.658 --> 34:22.593
-Can we talk?
-About what?

34:23.594 --> 34:24.962
About Alberto Lete.

34:26.664 --> 34:28.099
Who is he?

34:28.766 --> 34:30.301
You know.

34:31.169 --> 34:33.271
I was a sergeant in those days.

34:34.005 --> 34:35.973
I was about to become
a lieutenant.

34:37.108 --> 34:38.376
One day we got a call.

34:38.709 --> 34:41.379
There was a boy
lying at a railway crossing.

34:41.779 --> 34:44.248
He seemed to be dead.

34:44.315 --> 34:46.417
But he was breathing.

34:46.484 --> 34:47.752
So I called an ambulance.

34:47.819 --> 34:49.153
And they took him
to Clínicas hospital.

34:51.022 --> 34:53.191
The report says
he was hit by a car.

34:53.257 --> 34:56.561
-That he was drunk.
-Not my report.

34:56.627 --> 34:58.529
Who changed it then?

34:58.963 --> 35:00.131
I don't know.

35:00.465 --> 35:03.267
When I tried to find out,
my house got shot.

35:03.634 --> 35:06.170
Being a policeman,
I couldn't stand that.

35:06.571 --> 35:08.906
It seemed to be something big.

35:10.074 --> 35:12.276
I was too old to fight.

35:12.844 --> 35:14.612
So I asked to be discharged
and moved out here.

35:16.614 --> 35:17.915
But you never forgot it.

35:19.550 --> 35:20.785
Unfortunately, I didn't.

35:22.253 --> 35:24.722
I don't know
what you want to know.

35:25.656 --> 35:26.991
But be careful.

35:27.558 --> 35:29.694
I don't know what
this guy Lete knows either.

35:29.760 --> 35:31.129
But try not to end up like him.

35:34.532 --> 35:37.101
-Where should I go?
-You're asking me?

35:37.835 --> 35:41.639
I just don't know.
Try the "head" of the district.

35:43.007 --> 35:45.843
Nothing gets done
without his approval.

35:45.910 --> 35:47.411
Who is the head?
The police chief?

35:48.779 --> 35:50.348
Sometimes it is him.
Sometimes it isn't him.

35:50.681 --> 35:53.584
It should be the same person
who did it in your days.

35:54.152 --> 35:56.554
-Or maybe not.
-What about if he is?

35:59.190 --> 36:00.758
He is said to be
a wealthy guy.

36:01.959 --> 36:05.163
Who comes from Santa Rosa,
La Pampa.

36:05.596 --> 36:08.399
He runs some casinos
and deals with illegal gambling.

36:08.766 --> 36:11.335
These guys never show
their face.

36:12.904 --> 36:18.042
No, until someone shows it.

36:29.086 --> 36:31.389
Peque? Come here.

36:37.695 --> 36:38.796
It is today.
Can you make it?

36:39.130 --> 36:40.231
Of course.

36:41.332 --> 36:44.402
-Same place as before?
-Same place.

36:45.303 --> 36:46.537
Against who?

36:47.738 --> 36:49.340
I never give names.
But to you, I will.

36:49.941 --> 36:51.142
Vincen.

36:51.209 --> 36:52.410
You may know him.
He plays in another category.

36:52.476 --> 36:53.377
Older or younger?

36:53.744 --> 36:55.346
One or two years younger.

36:55.413 --> 36:56.547
But he seems older.
He is big.

36:56.948 --> 36:59.283
-Is he a champion?
-Yes, like you.

37:00.117 --> 37:01.352
What about the money?

37:02.186 --> 37:06.123
I may not get you 2,000,
but hopefully 1,000.

37:06.190 --> 37:08.859
-You must win, of course.
-I will.

37:09.460 --> 37:10.795
Go now.

37:27.445 --> 37:31.482
-Peque is doing very well.
-I am glad to hear that.

37:32.283 --> 37:33.684
He doesn't talk much,
but he has determination.

37:34.852 --> 37:36.320
How is he doing
here at the club?

37:36.654 --> 37:37.788
He is very enthusiastic.

37:38.155 --> 37:39.657
My daughter says he is happy.

37:42.994 --> 37:44.495
Your daughter?

37:44.562 --> 37:46.597
They live
in the same boarding house.

37:51.002 --> 37:52.670
Is there something wrong?

37:54.372 --> 37:55.906
No, nothing.

39:26.030 --> 39:26.931
Hello?

39:27.431 --> 39:28.466
Where are you?

39:28.532 --> 39:31.035
Far away.
Are you working tonight?

39:32.069 --> 39:34.472
No, it is my day off.
I'd like to see you.

39:35.005 --> 39:36.474
I can be in town in an hour.

39:37.641 --> 39:39.009
Where shall we meet?

39:40.010 --> 39:42.780
At my place.
I'll text you the address.

39:43.714 --> 39:45.916
-Fine.
-Bye.

40:35.733 --> 40:38.235
It is such a long time
since I don't collect stamps.

40:39.403 --> 40:41.739
-What championship is it?
-World Cup 1978.

40:42.873 --> 40:45.509
-Can I see them?
-No, they were my father's.

43:12.556 --> 43:16.760
-Is that your mom?
-Yes.

43:18.729 --> 43:21.365
She died five years ago.
Lung cancer.

43:27.137 --> 43:29.707
Did you know our last names
mean the same?

43:31.875 --> 43:33.477
Valrossa and Rosenthal.

43:34.411 --> 43:36.947
Both mean "valley of roses".

43:56.367 --> 43:57.701
It is a friend.
Stay here, please.

43:58.836 --> 44:00.170
What shall I do?
Get into the closet?

44:01.305 --> 44:04.441
No, you silly.
Keep quiet.

44:10.648 --> 44:14.451
There are some numbers
I don't like.

44:21.158 --> 44:22.326
What shall we do now?

44:23.861 --> 44:25.229
Make the call.

44:26.030 --> 44:27.631
Tell them to be careful.

44:31.535 --> 44:35.539
-A problem.
-Something wrong?

44:38.509 --> 44:41.445
I marked the addresses
of the seven kids on the map.

44:41.779 --> 44:43.280
All the accidents
were in the suburbs.

44:43.347 --> 44:44.448
But they all lived in town.

44:44.515 --> 44:45.649
Exactly.
They were almost neighbors.

44:46.316 --> 44:49.319
Soldati.
What is this?

44:49.753 --> 44:53.323
-Villa Riachuelo.
-Lugano, Piedrabuena.

44:53.390 --> 44:54.591
Lugano again.

44:56.060 --> 44:58.562
-What district is it?
-I think it is District Eight.

44:58.929 --> 45:01.932
District Eight...
And Los Piletones?

45:03.333 --> 45:05.369
District...Eight.

45:07.971 --> 45:09.940
Are you with someone?
I'll go away.

45:10.007 --> 45:11.842
No, don't go away.

45:11.909 --> 45:14.278
I was just told a co-worker
hit another boy.

45:15.212 --> 45:16.346
Let me out, please.

45:17.648 --> 45:20.017
Damn!
Come on.

45:48.879 --> 45:50.180
You have work to do.

45:56.487 --> 45:57.721
Don't worry.
